672
00:36:31,040 --> 00:36:32,949
and I'm afraid I couldn't attend today.

673
00:36:32,950 --> 00:36:36,759
Commandery Prince An, His Majesty has specifically instructed that

674
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:41,049
I have to take you to the palace even if I have to force you.

675
00:36:41,049 --> 00:36:43,669
But of course, if you don't want to go,

676
00:36:43,670 --> 00:36:45,909
I wouldn't dare to offend you.

677
00:36:45,910 --> 00:36:50,850
It'll be my honor if I'm punished because of this.

678
00:36:51,560 --> 00:36:54,629
But if you don't go today,

679
00:36:54,630 --> 00:36:59,360
His Majesty is worried that someone will eat you.

680
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:02,629
I don't know what that means.

681
00:37:02,630 --> 00:37:05,530
If anyone is confident that they can take it,

682
00:37:05,530 --> 00:37:07,900
