683
00:37:08,950 --> 00:37:12,149
By the way, Princess Xiping and Academician Xue

684
00:37:12,150 --> 00:37:14,189
are summoned to the palace, too.

685
00:37:14,190 --> 00:37:19,799
Commandery Prince An, if His Majesty hears this reply from you

686
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:22,460
