687
00:37:25,190 --> 00:37:27,519
I'm afraid it's not going to be easy for you.

688
00:37:27,520 --> 00:37:29,640
Thank you for reminding me.

689
00:37:30,360 --> 00:37:32,470
Please, Eunuch Qin.

690
00:37:33,710 --> 00:37:35,430
I'll take my leave now.

